description: This 400 Watt ATX12V 2.01 Dell PC Power Supply is a reliable upgrade or replacement for many compatible Dell computers (see compatible models below). It offers dual 12V power rails to deliver stable power to demanding components, as well as both 20 and 24-pin ATX motherboard power connectors and a generous number of component connectors to ensure broad system compatibility. Constructed of high quality components and designed to provide a long-lasting, durable power source for hard-working PCs, the 400 Watt ATX12V 2.01 Dell PC Power Supply is backed by StarTech.com's 2 year warranty and free lifetime technical support. The 400 Watt ATX12V 2.01 Dell PC Power Supply is compatible with standard ATX style versions of following: Dimension Series Models: 1100/2200/2300/ 2350/ 2400/4300/4400/4500/4550/4600/8200/8250/8300/8400/B100Optiplex Series Models: 170L/GX60/GX150/GX240/GX260/GX270Power Edge Series Models: 400SC/600SCPrecision Workstation Series Model: Model 340/350Smart Step Series Models: 100D/150D
title: StarTech PW400DELL 400 Watt ATX 12V 2.01 Dell Replacement Computer PC Power Supply ATX
